--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
This Software Development Kit (SDK) contains:
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

o Platform Support Package (PSP) source and pre-built Linux kernel
o U-Boot source and pre-built binary
o Matrix example applications including source code
o Code Composer Studio Version 5 (Eclipse-based IDE)
o Host Tools (Pin Mux Utility and Flash Tool)
o Environment setup scripts

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Environment Setup Script
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
The environment setup script installs all required software packages for the
Ubuntu Linux host and sets up the software development environment.
This script is run by entering the following commands at the Ubuntu Linux console.
(Use the directory name for your SDK platform).

cd ~/ti-sdk-am181x-evm-4.0.1.0
./setup.sh 

This script requires that the host machine be Ubuntu 10.04. If it is not then
the user will have to modify the scripts (located in the "bin" subdirectory to match 
their distribution type.  

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Installation Paths
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
By default, when this SDK is installed the following paths are set by the
installer based on the installation directory.

./Rules.make
    TI_SDK_PATH = Path to the root of this SDK
    CROSS_COMPILE = Path to ARM cross compiler with command prefix
    DESTDIR = Path to the root of the target file system

./linux-devkit/environment-setup
    SDK_PATH = Path to the root of the linux-devkit SDK
    TOOLCHAIN_PATH = Path to the ARM cross compiler  (Code Sourcery Lite 2009q1)

If you relocate this SDK installation after the installer has installed it
you will need to update the above paths to reflect the change in location.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Building the Matrix Example Applications
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Matrix is a Qt application that provides a Graphical User Interface (GUI) and
serves as the application launcher for the example applications.  The top-level
Makefile is located in the SDK installation directory and supports the following 
build commands.  

First change directory to your SDK install directory, for example:

cd /home/user/ti-sdk-am181x-evm-4.0.1.0

Enter the make commands shown below at the Ubuntu Linux host command line.

+----------------------------------+----------------------------------------------------+
| make clean                       | cleans all projects (debug and release versions)   |
|                                  |                                                    |
+----------------------------------+----------------------------------------------------+
| make all                         | Build debug and release versions of all projects.  |
|                                  | (For matrix_gui build the release version.)        |
+----------------------------------+----------------------------------------------------+
| make install                     | Copies release executable and all associated data  |
|                                  | files to target file system.                       |
+----------------------------------+----------------------------------------------------+
| make install_debug               | Copies debug executable and all associated data    |
|                                  | files to target file system.                       |
+----------------------------------+----------------------------------------------------+
 
+----------------------------------+----------------------------------------------------+
| make matrix_gui_clean            | cleans matrix_gui project (debug and release)      |
|                                  |                                                    |
+----------------------------------+----------------------------------------------------+
| make matrix_gui                  | Builds matrix_gui release version.                 |
|                                  |                                                    |
+----------------------------------+----------------------------------------------------+
| make matrix_gui_debug            | Builds matrix_gui debug version.                   |
|                                  |                                                    |
+----------------------------------+----------------------------------------------------+
| make matrix_gui_install          | Builds matrix_gui release version, copies          |
|                                  | executable and associated data files to target file|
|                                  | system. (Assumes release version was built last.)  |
+----------------------------------+----------------------------------------------------+
| make matrix_gui_install_debug    | Builds matrix_gui debug version, copies executable |
|                                  | and associated data files to target file system.   |
|                                  | (Assumes debug version was built last.)            |
+----------------------------------+----------------------------------------------------+
 
+----------------------------------+----------------------------------------------------+
| make matrix_tui_clean            | Cleans matrix_tui project (debug and release)      |
|                                  |                                                    |
+----------------------------------+----------------------------------------------------+
| make matrix_tui                  | Builds matrix_tui (debug and release)              |
|                                  |                                                    |
+----------------------------------+----------------------------------------------------+
| make matrix_tui_install          | Copies matrix_tui release version and associated   |
|                                  | data files to target file system                   |
+----------------------------------+----------------------------------------------------+
| make matrix_tui_install_debug    | Copies matrix_tui debug version and associated     |
|                                  | data files to target file system                   |
+----------------------------------+----------------------------------------------------+
 
+----------------------------------+----------------------------------------------------+
| make am_benchmarks_clean         | Cleans am_benchmarks project (debug and release)   |
|                                  |                                                    |
+----------------------------------+----------------------------------------------------+
| make am_benchmarks               | Builds am_benchmarks (debug and release)           |
|                                  |                                                    |
+----------------------------------+----------------------------------------------------+
| make am_benchmarks_install       | Copies am_benchmarks release version and associated|
|                                  | data files to target file system                   |
+----------------------------------+----------------------------------------------------+
| make am_benchmarks_install_debug | Copies am_benchmarks debug version and associated  |
|                                  | data files to target file system                   |
+----------------------------------+----------------------------------------------------+
 
+----------------------------------+----------------------------------------------------+
| make am_sysinfo_clean            | Cleans am_sysinfo project (debug and release)      |
|                                  |                                                    |
+----------------------------------+----------------------------------------------------+
| make am_sysinfo                  | Builds am_sysinfo (debug and release)              |
|                                  |                                                    |
+----------------------------------+----------------------------------------------------+
| make am_sysinfo_install          | Copies am_sysinfo release version and associated   |
|                                  | data files to target file system                   |
+----------------------------------+----------------------------------------------------+
| make am_sysinfo_install_debug    | Copies am_sysinfo debug version and associated     |
|                                  | data files to target file system                   |
+----------------------------------+----------------------------------------------------+
 

